              "free_text": [
                " Neutron produced via Li-7(p,n)Be-7 reaction on",
                " LiF targets. Proton beam about 100 uA. Proton",
                " energy was adjusted at 1912 keV. Neutrons were",
                " kinematically collimated in forward cone of 120 deg",
                " opening angle. Yielding neutron source strength",
                " 10**8 - 10**9 1/sec."
              ]
            }
          ],
